OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782762496
OL,3,CMultiple children suffer severe burns
OL,4,Cafter microwaving toys in TikTok trend
OL,6,FSeveral children have suffered serious
OL,7,Fburns after microwaving "squishy" toys
OL,8,Fin a new online trend.
OL,10,FSix children have been treated at the
OL,11,FRoyal Hospital for Children (RHC) in
OL,12,FGlasgow for injuries linked to the
OL,13,Ftrend in the past eight months, with
OL,14,Fsome needing surgery including skin
OL,15,Fgrafts.
OL,17,FVideos have circulated encouraging
OL,18,Fpeople to heat the toy in a microwave
OL,19,Fto make it softer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
