OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782762496
OL,3,CMultiple children suffer severe burns
OL,4,Cafter microwaving toys in TikTok trend
OL,6,FHowever, medical experts warn that
OL,7,Fthis can cause pressure to build
OL,8,Fmaking the gel inside explode, leading
OL,9,Fto severe burns.
OL,11,FJoseph Erskine, 8, from
OL,12,FClackmannanshire, needed weeks of
OL,13,Ftreatment and a skin graft after
OL,14,Fmicrowaving a squishy toy which then
OL,15,Fburst across his chest and hand in May.
OL,17,FHe now has to avoid direct sunlight to
OL,18,Fthe graft area for two years, and has
OL,19,Fhad to give up sports clubs and
OL,20,Factivities until he heals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
