FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782762496
OL,3,CMultiple children suffer severe burns
OL,4,Cafter microwaving toys in TikTok trend
OL,6,FHis mother Stephanie Ewing described
OL,7,Fwiping off the burning gel which had
OL,8,Ftaken off her son's skin.
OL,10,FShe expressed how "quick and easy" the
OL,11,Ftrend was and urged parents to
OL,12,Fdiscourage their children from doing
OL,13,Fthe same.
OL,15,F"We were shocked as it had never
OL,16,Fcrossed our minds that he would do
OL,17,Fthat with a toy," she said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
