PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782762496
OL,3,CMultiple children suffer severe burns
OL,4,Cafter microwaving toys in TikTok trend
OL,6,FScarlet Rowe, 11, from Irvine in North
OL,7,FAyrshire, was also treated for burns
OL,8,Fto her face and eyelid after a similar
OL,9,Fincident.
OL,11,FHer mother Gina described how they'd
OL,12,Fbought the squishy toy that day and
OL,13,Fweren't aware of how dangerous they
OL,14,Fcould be.
OL,16,FShe said: "We didn't realise what had
OL,17,Fhappened at first, it just looked like
OL,18,Fslime on her face.
OL,26,@xD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
