PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782762496
OL,3,CMultiple children suffer severe burns
OL,4,Cafter microwaving toys in TikTok trend
OL,6,F"It was only after a few minutes we
OL,7,Frealised it had been heated and was
OL,8,Fburning her skin."
OL,10,FThe colourful toys are made from a
OL,11,Fflexible material, such as silicone,
OL,12,Fthat allows them to be moulded into
OL,13,Fdifferent shapes.
OL,15,FBurns specialists said injuries caused
OL,16,Fby heated squishy toys can be
OL,17,Fparticularly severe because the gel
OL,18,Finside can remain extremely hot and
OL,19,Fget stuck to the skin, prolonging the
OL,20,Fburn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
