PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1782762496
OL,3,CMultiple children suffer severe burns
OL,4,Cafter microwaving toys in TikTok trend
OL,6,FSharon Ramsay, a burns nurse at the
OL,7,FRHC, said these cases are becoming
OL,8,Fincreasingly more common.
OL,10,FShe said some children have been left
OL,11,Fwith "permanent scarring" and that
OL,12,Fsome injuries are so severe that they
OL,13,Frequire long-term treatment, surgery
OL,14,Fand rehabilitation.
OL,16,FHealing and recovery from burns can
OL,17,Ftake weeks or months and children who
OL,18,Fsuffer them often need ongoing care
OL,19,Fincluding dressings, physiotherapy and
OL,20,Fscar management.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
